  "text": "The pathophysiology of PRES as well as the occurrence of cytotoxic foci in PRES is still not completely understood and there are two opposing theories which are discussed controversially in the literature with theory 1 being more popular at present [CITATION_1] : 1. Hypertension with consecutive failed autoregulation and hyperperfusion. 2. Vasoconstriction with consecutive hypoperfusion and ischemia.",
